Machine Learning APIs

Serverless & no coding required

Transcribe - audio -> text
Polly - text -> audio
Lex - chatbot
Translate - text language translation
Comprehend Textract - NLP
Rekognition - images

-------------------------------------------------------------------

Lex

Intent - the bot's goal
Utterances - from user, invokes intent
Slots - specified data that the bot needs to fulfil intent
Prompts - questions the bot will ask to get data
Fulfillment - bot registers that all slots are filled (i.e. has all required data) and triggers something else (likely an AWS Lambda function)

Can handle text NLP
Can handle text-to-speech due to integration with Amazon Polly (https://aws.amazon.com/polly/)

You can specify how it handles errors too
